            </description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">钱程</dc:creator><pubDate>Sun, 16 Apr 2023 15:47:53 +0800</pubDate><guid>http://www.zhihu.com/question/588023318/answer/2986416239</guid></item><item><title>你为什么想去伯利兹旅行？</title><link>http://www.zhihu.com/question/465800979/answer/2982676613?utm_campaign=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_source=rss&amp;utm_content=title</link><description>&lt;p data-pid="ZQi55Isp"&gt;2020年春节去了伯利兹和危地马拉，去伯利兹的动机是大蓝洞，去危地马拉则主要看TIKAL玛雅遗址。然而中美洲的鸟况如此之好，我们走着走着差不多把行程走成了观鸟路线。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-pid="z-xYWiz8"&gt;我们在&lt;b&gt;伯利兹城&lt;/b&gt;的第一晚和最后一晚都住在华美达酒店。听闻城里治安不太好，所以我们并没太走远，只在酒店附近活动。酒店庭院里就有鹦鹉和啄木鸟可看，海边则有笑鸥和褐鹈鹕飞来飞去。它们都不甚怕人。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-447a20206900d214d89c7852fc68d652_720w.jpeg?source=b1748391?rss" data-caption="笑鸥" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="5760" data-rawheight="3840" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-447a20206900d214d89c7852fc68d652" data-watermark-src="v2-b6f2c88cdab651f68510e3ff04128495" data-private-watermark-src="" data-original-token="v2-447a20206900d214d89c7852fc68d652" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-6db5971295058e84a1de87700a8e1413_720w.jpeg?source=b1748391?rss" data-caption="褐鹈鹕" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="2772" data-rawheight="4460" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-6db5971295058e84a1de87700a8e1413" data-watermark-src="v2-4e3a94c1e7ef833755ab012801129f5e" data-private-watermark-src="" data-original-token="v2-6db5971295058e84a1de87700a8e1413" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-d137a0940e3db307f9e45ba3b34b5124_720w.jpeg?source=b1748391?rss" data-caption="热带小嘲鸫" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="3120" data-rawheight="2152" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-d137a0940e3db307f9e45ba3b34b5124" data-watermark-src="v2-8ec75f86e49a4f9ddaf72937625609e9" data-private-watermark-src="" data-original-token="v2-d137a0940e3db307f9e45ba3b34b5124" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-2758f61654d0ea6e8934749bb66a2bc2_720w.jpeg?source=b1748391?rss" data-caption="绿喉鹦哥" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="1517" data-rawheight="2378" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-2758f61654d0ea6e8934749bb66a2bc2" data-watermark-src="v2-2da09bf53e2440ba678695dc431b94c7" data-private-watermark-src="" data-original-token="v2-2758f61654d0ea6e8934749bb66a2bc2" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-a14865d32b0786e0309ed0e4f7fc6947_720w.jpeg?source=b1748391?rss" data-caption="大尾拟八哥" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="3635" data-rawheight="2527" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-a14865d32b0786e0309ed0e4f7fc6947" data-watermark-src="v2-100a8b90c389a316218564f9e847017a" data-private-watermark-src="" data-original-token="v2-a14865d32b0786e0309ed0e4f7fc6947" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-423589ead5bfdf5c240a8a43159f5020_720w.jpeg?source=b1748391?rss" data-caption="翻石鹬" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="3487" data-rawheight="2378" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-423589ead5bfdf5c240a8a43159f5020" data-watermark-src="v2-4241cbb58e345abdc2df0081702e4efe" data-private-watermark-src="" data-original-token="v2-423589ead5bfdf5c240a8a43159f5020" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-70f71c95678cf78dcdae804407af4b65_720w.jpeg?source=b1748391?rss" data-caption="金额啄木鸟" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="2138" data-rawheight="3332" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-70f71c95678cf78dcdae804407af4b65" data-watermark-src="v2-40106195e0320398935996531d5460dd" data-private-watermark-src="" data-original-token="v2-70f71c95678cf78dcdae804407af4b65" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p data-pid="NJYi1als"&gt;整个伯利兹地广人稀，公路旁多半是原始丛林，偶见甘蔗地和油棕林。老司机一路指点我们这超市中国人开的，那厂房中国人盖的。当然这中国多半是海峡那边，一个中国，各自表述啦。中午到了&lt;b&gt;CROOKED TREE LAGOON&lt;/b&gt;。这个潟湖是我利用组织者特权特意加进去的景点，果然没来错。湖上各种水鸟令人目不暇接，岸边草地上和农田里则是各种小鸟，酒店本身有蜂鸟喂食器，另外附近的森林也值得好好探索一番。认真观鸟的话，在这里住上个两三天也值得。我们吃过饭就坐船巡游，LP 上说的船嘴鹭，黑领鹰，食螺鸢统统看到，五种鱼狗（KINGFISHER）见到四种。因为看鸟看得容易又热闹，连不是鸟友的小伙伴们也大呼过瘾，大有入坑的趋势。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-16dd6956cbd010ed1fc1b7f5fe25bed4_720w.jpeg?source=b1748391?rss" data-caption="朱红霸鹟" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="1870" data-rawheight="2979" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-16dd6956cbd010ed1fc1b7f5fe25bed4" data-watermark-src="v2-9bafd4add0c4c7d02b926a77e7ee51a8" data-private-watermark-src="" data-original-token="v2-16dd6956cbd010ed1fc1b7f5fe25bed4" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-0d6adc0701cd856ec018feabfbbb81ac_720w.jpeg?source=b1748391?rss" data-caption="美洲水雉" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="3367" data-rawheight="2534" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-0d6adc0701cd856ec018feabfbbb81ac" data-watermark-src="v2-9a1f3388ad7977f5b7097c90ac616f62" data-private-watermark-src="" data-original-token="v2-0d6adc0701cd856ec018feabfbbb81ac" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-8c97cf0a40365bb3d5526e7b55f85f83_720w.jpeg?source=b1748391?rss" data-caption="灰颈林秧鸡" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="5760" data-rawheight="3840" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-8c97cf0a40365bb3d5526e7b55f85f83" data-watermark-src="v2-b5b9266ee565bf93e3699cc738232d82" data-private-watermark-src="" data-original-token="v2-8c97cf0a40365bb3d5526e7b55f85f83" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-107c486c8721582a5e60671b46f8192d_720w.jpeg?source=b1748391?rss" data-caption="中美食籽雀" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="1863" data-rawheight="2929" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-107c486c8721582a5e60671b46f8192d" data-watermark-src="v2-849644b232ab9c743f1910dfb314ca04" data-private-watermark-src="" data-original-token="v2-107c486c8721582a5e60671b46f8192d" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-041aea828abd9445f7a1295c2a8a4a9a_720w.jpeg?source=b1748391?rss" data-caption="食螺鸢" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="1722" data-rawheight="2710" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-041aea828abd9445f7a1295c2a8a4a9a" data-watermark-src="v2-8906ffa8330bcda9b64205b8669c546b" data-private-watermark-src="" data-original-token="v2-041aea828abd9445f7a1295c2a8a4a9a" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-4fc9086a4289b684b54f6e61ac28cded_720w.jpeg?source=b1748391?rss" data-caption="黑领鹰" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="1877" data-rawheight="2880" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-4fc9086a4289b684b54f6e61ac28cded" data-watermark-src="v2-56a76c58497b99127582a9349f9ae229" data-private-watermark-src="" data-original-token="v2-4fc9086a4289b684b54f6e61ac28cded" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-9ac49e59661d32d5f8e6703b0408bd77_720w.jpeg?source=b1748391?rss" data-caption="船嘴鹭" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="2047" data-rawheight="3190" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-9ac49e59661d32d5f8e6703b0408bd77" data-watermark-src="v2-d63076d987642a58bd21b1b04446a517" data-private-watermark-src="" data-original-token="v2-9ac49e59661d32d5f8e6703b0408bd77" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b5609295a082c998d10d6584478abad7_720w.jpeg?source=b1748391?rss" data-caption="栗腹鹭" data-size="normal" data-rawwidth="1347" data-rawheight="2100" data-watermark="watermark" data-original-src="v2-b5609295a082c998d10d6584478abad7" data-watermark-src="v2-f691e679127c23d6498b4137007962cf" data-private-watermark-src="" data-original-token="v2-b5609295a082c998d10d6584478abad7" style="max-width: 400px;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="https://picx.zhimg